  <brief_title>Gefitinib (Iressa) in Combo With Chemoradiation in Patients With Locally Advanced Head &amp; Neck Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I/II Trial of ZD1839 (Iressa) Given Concurrently With Cisplatin and Radiotherapy in Patients With Locally Advanced Head and Neck Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
